    <segment id="296">, a Guerra CivilOnde YouTube (52 min.)Direção</segment>
    <segment id="297">Eduardo EscorelLink:</segment>
    <segment id="298">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U2aFvcDVc1k A Guerra dos PaulistasOnde YouTube (55 min.)Direção Laís Bodanzky e Luiz BolognesiLink: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PlV0ojKO6wg</segment>
  </rst>
</analysis>